◆ unpack_nal_start

unsigned pjmedia_h264_packetizer_cfg::unpack_nal_start

NAL start code size used for unpacketizing. Valid options are 3 (0, 0, 1) or 4 (0, 0, 0, 1). Default: 3 (0, 0, 1)
